{"tid":305760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七一回歸盃】剛慶祝完60大壽 足球名宿鄧劍棟踢波暈倒不治","createTime":"2017-07-02T03:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T07:53:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23eb80a5ad57588e4f6bbb10de108acf4c449d1c","tid":305760,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 70年代足球名宿，有「加山三劍俠」稱號的退役球員鄧劍棟，昨晨參加「七一回歸盃」足球賽途中不適暈倒，送院搶救後，延至今日凌晨零時38分不治。<br />\n<br />\n今日凌晨零時許，鄧劍棟波友的WhatsApp群組已傳出鄧腦幹死亡，只有輕微心跳，多名友人事後立即趕往醫院了解情況。鄧的前隊友麥永才，前晚才參加過鄧的60歲生日晚宴，今早獲悉鄧命危的消息，亦趕往醫院了解情況，但被醫護人員告知鄧已被搬離深切治療部病房，當時麥仍未得知鄧的死訊，還致電聯絡鄧的家人了解最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n鄧劍棟昨晨在灣仔修頓球場以元老隊身份參加「七一回歸盃」足球賽時，疑因天氣酷熱，加上前晚參加家人為他而設的60歲生日晚宴致休息不足，最終在比賽中途疑中暑不適，被換出休息期間突然暈倒，一度沒有呼吸脈搏。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170702/56903984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170702%2F56903984&d=e3ajFMWzfO%2FATASwrcDSbL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4d88d516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170702%2F56903984&h=c265dc7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170702/56903984</a>"},{"pid":"118f7187c17fb6bb8fdb2b348c65324d2b89f566","tid":305760,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d47d8c1c476d161ae377fef36aec4e11569298f","tid":305760,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea8bc6c80095faa65cacbf42252e9d83b134d5d","tid":305760,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"抵死，及早拜見毛主席"},{"pid":"af27ede5baf2701edde660709adef2b2d1d1d7e4","tid":305760,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"家人應該告誤殺"},{"pid":"583fb80890c3134efed56a435dbc74863593e2b9","tid":305760,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"喜獲偉大既毛主席召見！"},{"pid":"68cd40168d1753dd1b545d3aeaf6d6568eacb4db","tid":305760,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"落去見老毛"},{"pid":"ddf84d8038a13cc14470c57f2799298afc9d9390","tid":305760,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"人民英雄<br />\n捨身為七一"}]}